com.emitrom.flash4j.flex.client.mx.bindings

Class BindingUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emitrom.flash4j.core.client.ProxyObject
      • com.emitrom.flash4j.flex.client.mx.bindings.BindingUtils

  • public class BindingUtils
extends ProxyObject
    The BindingUtils class defines utility methods for performing data binding from ActionScript. You can use the methods defined in this class to configure data bindings.
